arts.ttl: Matty Godden goal sends Charlton Athletic to Wembley - as top scorer’s finish defeats Wycombe Wanderers
arts.sum: Lloyd Jones headed a glorious chance wide of goal in the 38th minute from close range from Godden’s cross. Charlton Athletic are heading to Wembley in the League One play-off final after Matty Godden’s 22nd goal of the season was enough to defeat Wycombe Wanderers at The Valley.

arts.ttl: Matty Godden’s late strike sends Charlton into League One play-off final
arts.sum: Godden scrambled the only goal over the two legs after 171 minutes of attritional football.
